{"synckey":1713426189,"updated":[{"bookId":"908306","bookmarkId":"908306_6_5054-5131","chapterUid":34,"markText":"其次，有趣是一种愉悦感。带来愉快的意外感，让人觉得“有趣”；带来不快的意外感，只会让人觉得愤怒。","range":"4870-4947","createTime":1634274093,"type":1},{"bookId":"908306","bookmarkId":"908306_6_4756-4844","chapterUid":34,"markText":"本质上，“有趣”是一场令人愉悦的意外，是一种无关功利的惊喜。首先，有趣是一种意外。别人认为你本应该是这样的，而你不是。","range":"4572-4660","createTime":1634274080,"type":1},{"bookId":"908306","bookmarkId":"908306_6_1953-1987","chapterUid":34,"markText":"我觉得跑步很爽，所以去跑步，一天不跑我就难受——这会让跑步变得有趣。","range":"1763-1797","createTime":1634273993,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"1.2 有趣是个什么东西","chapterUid":34,"chapterIdx":8}],"book":{"bookId":"908306","version":160270294,"format":"epub","soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/44/yuewen_908306/s_yuewen_9083061721797710.jpg","title":"如何成为一个有趣的人","author":"王小圈","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"K%R:4eV[xuo,j?j]oqoyWB","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#251c00"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#281c00"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#2c1b00"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#383103"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#3b3100"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#3d3100"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#50481d"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#524800"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#544800"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#564900"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#6c6112"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#6f6100"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#69612f"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#8a7b00"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#837a47"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#897b00"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#9d9560"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#a19543"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#a4951f"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#a79500"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#beaf3e"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#c1af04"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#c2af00"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#d2ca90"},{"key":"8/6","hex":"#d6ca74"},{"key":"8/12","hex":"#deca00"},{"key":"9/2","hex":"#e9e4c2"},{"key":"9/12","hex":"#fae614"},{"key":"1/100","hex":"#a4951f"},{"key":"2/100","hex":"#beaf3e"},{"key":"3/100","hex":"#ffffff"},{"key":"4/100","hex":"#F3F1E5"},{"key":"5/100","hex":"#F3F1E5"},{"key":"6/100","hex":"#271E00"}],"dominat